# I successfully harvested another 10 units of iron ore, bringing my total to 10 iron ore in my inventory.
# 
# Now, I can return to the stone furnace and insert the iron ore to continue the smelting process for producing iron plates.
# 
# Let's proceed with inserting 5 iron ore into the furnace again.

insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, furnace, quantity=5)  # Inserting 5 iron ore into the furnace.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Displaying updated inventory after insertion.
